WEBVTT

00:12:57.438 --> 00:13:01.142
Wash your hands when you go into a meeting
and when you come out of a meeting.

00:13:01.166 --> 00:13:03.454
Get rituals that are based
around handwashing.

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:06.014
Sanitize your phone.

00:13:06.038 --> 00:13:09.819
You touch that phone with your dirty,
unwashed hands all the time.

00:13:09.843 --> 00:13:12.271
I know you take it
into the bathroom with you.

00:13:12.295 --> 00:13:14.446
(Laughter)

00:13:15.264 --> 00:13:20.314
So sanitize your phone and consider
not using it as often in public.

00:13:20.338 --> 00:13:23.459
Maybe TikTok and Instagram
can be home things only.

00:13:24.550 --> 00:13:25.857
Don't touch your face.

00:13:26.888 --> 00:13:28.538
Don't rub your eyes.

00:13:28.562 --> 00:13:30.014
Don't bite your fingernails.